snippet.title: Mantis Burn Racing® - Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
Mantis Burn Racing® is 'the finest overhead racer in years' check out what critics are saying about 'one of the indie finds of the year' in the official accolades trailer.

#MantisBurnRacing is out now on PlayStation®4, Xbox One and Steam® (for Windows PC). Official website: http://bit.ly/2aS4fu4
